# Exclude the live blog domain — canonical URLs and OG meta tags in newly generated
# pages point to blog.csmac.nz/Vibeblogging/ before the post has been published,
# so lychee would fail on any PR that adds a new post. These links are validated
# implicitly by the deploy workflow once the site is live.
^https://blog\.csmac\.nz/Vibeblogging/
